Maintainer: Daniel James <daniel@64studio.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), autotools-dev, portaudio19-dev, libflac-dev, libvorbis-dev, libfltk1.1-dev, libjpeg-dev, libmp3lame-dev, libopus-dev, libpng12-dev, libsamplerate0-dev, zlib1g-dev, libxft-dev, libfontconfig1-dev, libxinerama-dev
