Package: butt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Easy to use, multi OS streaming tool
 butt (broadcast using this tool) is an easy to use, multi OS streaming tool. 
 It supports ShoutCast and IceCast. At the moment you can't feed butt directly 
 with audio files.
 Features:
  * Streaming and recording simultaneously with different bitrates 
  * Switchable lcd informations (left mouse on the display) 
  * Automatic reconnection 
